== Static terrain ==
- Remapping heightmap to CyberSpaceObject dimension
- CyberspaceObjects merge into 1 mesh
    - simplifier when scale Y is same
    - full mesh data consolidation under 1 terrain object
- When hex scales, scale grid
- random scale offset (Gaetan) [noise]
-

== Dynamic terrain ==
- Shader based edge movement of terrain

== Effects ==
- Fog
-

== Tools ==
- Spline tool
    - Generate objects around  spline
        - make objects dynamically move around it
